INSERT INTO `pj_products_service` VALUES (1,1,1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','Random Width/Random Length Lumber','PJ Lumber supplies large volumes of FAS and 1C White Oak in 4/4, 5/4, 6/4, and 8/4 thicknesses. We also supply FAS and 1C, 4/4-8/4 in Red Oak and Southern White Ash. Inspected piece by piece, our lumber is guaranteed to be on-grade and of the highest quality on the market.','images/phocagallery/123/pj lumber 64 of 85.jpg','images/phocagallery/123/pj lumber 64 of 85.jpg'),(3,3,1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','Sawn Veneer','With 10 Wintersteiger frame saws, PJ Lumber is ready to do the custom cutting you need. We can cut 3&rdquo;-8&rdquo; wide material of all species, though as with the lumber, our specialty is White Oak.','images/phocagallery/123/pj lumber 44 of 85.jpg','images/phocagallery/123/pj lumber 44 of 85.jpg'),(2,2,1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','Ripped To Width  Strips','Running 7 rip saws daily, PJ Lumber offers fixed width strips in Rustic and FAS grades with 4/4 White oak and in FAS with 5/4 White Oak.  We also supply some fixed width FAS strips in Red Oak and Ash.  Our 4/4 FAS White Oak strips are offered 3&rdquo;-12&rdquo;, full container volumes available in each width.','images/phocagallery/123/pj lumber 30 of 85.jpg','images/phocagallery/123/pj lumber 30 of 85.jpg'),(4,4,1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','Solid Flooring','T&G, end-matched, we can supply the big and small jobs of solid White Oak flooring, and with our extensive selection of wide plank White Oak lumber on hand, we can get the job done quickly.  As with all of our other products, our flooring is prepped for export or domestic.','images/phocagallery/123/pj lumber 52 of 85.jpg','images/phocagallery/123/pj lumber 52 of 85.jpg'),(5,5,1,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','Custom Storage','Our close proximity to the Port makes PJ Lumber an excellent place to store your material while you wait on the next ship.  Specializing in the storage of forest products, we know how to keep your material safe and dry.  We also supply the custom markings you may need in final preparation of shipment.','images/phocagallery/123/pj lumber 70 of 85.jpg','images/phocagallery/123/pj lumber 70 of 85.jpg');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `pj_products_service` ENABLE KEYS */;
